metadata.name: Hard Work Pays Off
metadata.description:
this is Franky the frog. Franky has been working really hard to provide for his wife and kids. that's what makes him happy, a simple frog really. knowing his family has a roof under their heads, food on their plates, and a sense of security is what makes Franky the happiest.

Franky goes to work with a smile on his face, and comes back from work with that same smile. that's the type of frog Franky is. 



Franky asks, "what are you working for?"
